        .thumbnail
          img(src="../../images/phpd83ivxAM.jpg")
          .caption
            h3 Women Who Code
            p Check out the Women Who Code Meetup.  The Denver/Boulder chapter has the 2nd largest contingent in the country.
            p 
              a.btn.btn-primary(href='http://womenwhocode.com' role='button') Go to Women Who Code!

      .col-xs-6.col-sm-3
        .thumbnail
          img(src="../../images/women20.png")
          .caption
            h3 Women 2.0
